DL_POLY is a parallel molecular dynamics simulation package developed
at Daresbury Laboratory by W. Smith and T.R. Forester under the
auspices of the former Engineering and Physical Sciences Research
Council (EPSRC) for the EPSRC's Collaborative Computational Project
for the Computer Simulation of Condensed Phases (CCP5) and the
Advanced Research Computing Group (ARCG) at Daresbury Laboratory.  The
package is the property of The Council for the Central Laboratory of
the Research Councils (CCLRC).
